INSERT INTO `price_review` (`review_id`, `mobile_id`, `overview`, `review`, `created_at`) VALUES
(1, 1, 'Vivo Y16 â€“ Compact Performance with Long-Lasting Battery\r\nVivo Y16 features a 6.51-inch HD+ IPS LCD display with a Full-View waterdrop notch for vibrant visuals. It comes with dual rear cameras of 13MP + 2MP, featuring autofocus, LED flash, and Full HD video recording. The 5MP front camera ensures bright and clear selfies. Under the hood, it is powered by a Mediatek Helio P35 (12 nm) chipset with an octa-core CPU up to 2.3 GHz. The PowerVR GE8320 GPU ensures smooth everyday performance. The phone offers 3GB or 4GB RAM and 32GB or 64GB internal storage, expandable via a dedicated MicroSD slot. Stay powered all day with the 5000 mAh battery and 10W fast charging.\r\nSecurity is seamless with a side-mounted fingerprint sensor and face unlock. Dual SIM support and FM Radio add extra convenience.\r\n', 'Official Price: BDT 13,999 (4GB RAM + 64GB Storage)\r\n\r\nSpecifications\r\nâ€¢ Display: 6.51-inch HD+ IPS LCD\r\nâ€¢ Processor: MediaTek Helio P35 (12nm)\r\nâ€¢ RAM: 3GB / 4GB\r\nâ€¢ Storage: 32GB / 64GB (expandable up to 1TB via MicroSD)\r\nâ€¢ Camera: 13MP + 2MP (rear), 5MP (front)\r\nâ€¢ Battery: 5000mAh\r\nâ€¢ OS: Funtouch OS 12 (Android 12)\r\nâ€¢ Fingerprint Sensor: Side-mounted\r\nâ€¢ Colors: Drizzling Gold, Stellar Black\r\n\r\nPros\r\nâ€¢ Stylish Design: Premium finish with an attractive look.\r\nâ€¢ Long-lasting Battery: 5000mAh battery supports extended usage.\r\nâ€¢ User-friendly UI: Funtouch OS 12 is simple and customizable.\r\nâ€¢ Good Camera Performance: 13MP main camera with HDR mode for quality photos.\r\n\r\nCons\r\nâ€¢ Processor Performance: Helio P35 is slightly outdated, may struggle with heavy gaming or multitasking.\r\nâ€¢ Fast Charging: Supports 18W fast charging, but comes with a 10W charger in the box.\r\nâ€¢ Display Brightness: Direct sunlight visibility could be challenging.\r\n\r\nSummary\r\nVivo Y16 is a budget-friendly smartphone suitable for everyday use. Its stylish design, long-lasting battery, and user-friendly features make it a good choice for general users. However, for heavy gaming or intensive multitasking, other alternatives might be better.\r\n', '2025-10-04 18:52:31'),
(2, 2, 'Xiaomi Mix 4 Price in Bangladesh October 2025\r\nThe Xiaomi Mix 4 is now available in Bangladesh with 128GB, 256GB, and 512GB variants along with 8GB or 12GB RAM. Xiaomi Mix 4â€™s Price is 68000 taka. Xiaomi Mix 4 features a powerful 4500mAh battery with 120W fast charging support, ensuring super-quick power-up. It runs on Android 11 and is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 888+ 5G (5 nm) chipset for ultra-fast performance.\r\n', 'Xiaomi Mix 4 offers several features that make it worth the investment. From a triple rear camera setup (108MP+8MP+13MP) and a 20MP under-display selfie camera to 8K video recording, 4500mAh battery with fast charging, 5G support, dual SIM, and additional features like WLAN, Bluetooth, FM Radio, USB port, Face Unlock, and under-display fingerprint sensor, Mix 4 delivers top-tier performance. Price-wise, Xiaomi Mix 4 is positioned as a high-end device, offering these flagship features at a competitive cost compared to other premium smartphones in the market, making it a smart choice for tech enthusiasts seeking value for money.\r\n\r\nOur Verdict:\r\nXiaomi Mix 4 is one of the best 5G smartphones under 70K Taka. If you love online games like Free Fire or PUBG MOBILE, Xiaomi Mix 4 phone is perfect with its 8GB/12GB RAM and Qualcomm SM8350 Snapdragon 888+ 5G (5nm) processor, delivering smooth and lag-free performance. The 4500mAh battery with fast charging ensures long-lasting usage without frequent charging. Its quad-camera setup with a 108MP primary sensor captures stunning photos and videos, while 5G support guarantees fast and reliable network connectivity. With a perfect blend of powerful performance, excellent camera quality, strong battery, and modern features, the Xiaomi Mix 4 is a top choice for gamers and tech enthusiasts looking for value for money.\r\n', '2025-10-05 06:39:45'),
(3, 3, 'Xiaomi Mix Flip Price in Bangladesh June 2025\r\nThe Xiaomi Mix Flip is now available in Bangladesh with 12GB of RAM and 256GB Storage. Xiaomi Mix Flip Price is 1,00,000 taka(Expected). Xiaomi Mix Flip features a powerful 4,780mAh battery with 67W fast charging support, ensuring super-quick power-up. Xiaomiâ€™s HyperOS, based on Android 14 and is powered by the Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chipset for ultra-fast performance. Xiaomi Mix Flip 4.01-inch AMOLED outer display and a 6.86-inch AMOLED inner screen, Dolby Vision and HDR10+ content. Available in Black and Purple colors.\r\n', 'The Xiaomi MIX Flip is a premium foldable smartphone featuring a 6.86-inch LTPO OLED display, Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor, and a 50MP Leica camera. From camera setup (50MP main + 12MP ultra-wide) 4K video recording, 4780mAh battery with 67W fast charging, 5G support, dual SIM, and additional features like WLAN, Bluetooth 5.3, FM Radio, USB port, Face Unlock, and under-display fingerprint sensor. Price-wise, Xiaomi MIX Flip stands out as a premium foldable smartphone. Price-wise, itâ€™s positioned in the high-end category, delivering flagship performance, making it a smart choice for tech enthusiasts seeking value for money.\r\n\r\nOur Verdict:\r\nXiaomi MIX Flip feels like a perfect balance between style and power. Performance Powered by the Snapdragon 8 Gen 3, it runs super smooth whether youâ€™re gaming, streaming, or multitasking. The Leica dual camera vibrant photos, and the 6.86-inch OLED display makes everything look stunningly clear. Battery life is solid thanks to the 4780mAh capacity and 67W fast charging, so you can get back to 100% in no time. Overall, the MIX Flip brings the premium foldable experience to users who love cutting-edge tech but still care about elegance and comfort in hand. Itâ€™s a stylish flagship that actually delivers what it promises.\r\n', '2025-10-05 10:56:57'),
(4, 5, 'Xiaomi Mix Fold 3â€“ Price and Specs in Bangladesh\r\nThe Xiaomi Mix Fold 3 is Xiaomiâ€™s thinnest and most durable foldable smartphone, combining style, innovation, and top-notch performance. It features an 8.03-inch foldable LTPO OLED+ display with a 120Hz refresh rate. Powered by the SnapdragonÂ® 8 Gen 2 chipset with Adreno 740 GPU, the Mix Fold 3 Android 13, it offers user experience  Photography is impressive with a quad-camera setup: a 50MP main sensor, two 10MP telephoto lenses, and a 12MP ultrawide lens, complemented by a 20MP front camera for sharp selfie. The device is backed by a 4800 mAh battery with 67W fast charging, keeping you powered throughout the day. The Xiaomi Mix Fold 3 price in Bangladesh starts at BDT 230,000 for the variant with 12GB RAM and 256GB storage. Available in Black and Gold colors.\r\n', 'Xiaomi Mix Fold 3 Price Review in Bangladesh\r\nThe Xiaomi Mix Fold 3 is one of the most premium foldable smartphones available in Bangladesh, starting at BDT 230,000. With its stunning design, ultra-slim body, and strong build quality, it delivers an exceptional flagship experience. The Leica quad camera setup ensures professional-level photography, while the Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor guarantees top-tier performance with speed and efficiency.\r\nIts dual AMOLED display (cover + foldable) offers vibrant visuals and smooth multitasking, perfect for both entertainment and productivity. The device also features a VC liquid cooling system to maintain optimal temperature during heavy use, ensuring lag-free gaming and multitasking.\r\nMoreover, the optimized 4800mAh battery with 67W fast charging provides long-lasting power and quick refueling. Though the Mix Fold 3 doesnâ€™t come with official water resistance certification, its strong build quality still ensures a reliable level of protection for everyday use.\r\nOverall Verdict:\r\nThe Xiaomi Mix Fold 3 is an ultra-premium foldable phone combining beauty, strength, and power. Itâ€™s ideal for users who want innovation, elegance, and performance in one device.\r\n', '2025-10-05 15:55:42'),
(5, 6, 'The Samsung Galaxy J5 (2015) features a 5-inch Super AMOLED display with a 720x1280 pixel resolution, delivering sharp and vibrant visuals. Powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 410 chipset, this device packs a 1.2 GHz quad-core Cortex-A53 CPU and Adreno 306 GPU, ensuring smooth performance for everyday tasks and light gaming. It comes with 1.5 GB of RAM and 8GB or 16GB internal storage options, expandable via microSD card. The 13 MP rear camera with f/1.9 aperture captures bright and clear photos, while the 5 MP front camera with LED flash is perfect for selfies, even in low light. Running on Android 5.1 (Lollipop) and upgradable to Android 6.0.1 (Marshmallow), the J5 offers a clean and easy-to-use interface. Connectivity features include Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Bluetooth 4.1, GPS, and NFC (depending on market). It also supports FM radio and microUSB 2.0. The device is powered by a removable 2600 mAh battery, providing decent backup for a full day of usage. With a glass front and plastic body, the Galaxy J5 maintains a light and comfortable build â€” weighing 146 grams and measuring 142.1 x 71.8 x 7.9 mm.\r\nAvailable in White, Black, and Gold, the Samsung Galaxy J5 price in Bangladesh is BDT 13,990 for the 1.5GB RAM + 8GB storage variant.\r\n', 'The Samsung Galaxy J5 (2015) is one of Samsungâ€™s most reliable budget smartphones. Priced at BDT 13,990 in Bangladesh, it delivers a balanced mix of performance, camera quality, and stylish design. With its 5-inch Super AMOLED HD display, the J5 provides vibrant colors and great sunlight visibility a rare feature in this price range. Powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 410 processor and 1.5GB RAM, it handles daily tasks, social media, and light gaming smoothly. The 13MP rear camera (f/1.9) captures bright and detailed photos, while the 5MP front camera with LED flash makes it ideal for selfies, even in low light. Battery performance is impressive for its category the 2600 mAh removable battery offers a full day of backup. Users also appreciate the option to replace the battery when needed, which adds to its long-term usability. Design-wise, the Galaxy J5 feels premium for its price, featuring a glass front, plastic back, and 7.9mm slim body. Itâ€™s available in White, Black, and Gold colors. Running on Android 5.1 Lollipop (upgradable to Marshmallow), it provides a smooth and user-friendly interface. Considering its features, camera quality, and performance, the Samsung Galaxy J5 (2015) remains one of the best budget Samsung phones of its era perfect for users who want reliability, simplicity, and value.\r\nThe Samsung Galaxy J5 (2015) offers excellent value for money. Itâ€™s perfect for students, first-time smartphone users, or anyone who needs a dependable device with good camera quality and battery life at an affordable price.', '2025-10-05 17:10:29'),
(6, 7, 'The Oppo A6 Pro 5G is fast 5G connectivity, long-lasting battery life, Launched in Bangladesh in 2025, Oppo A6 Pro 5G is a 7000mAh battery with 80W SUPERVOOC fast charging. IP69 water and dust resistance provides reliability in daily use, Oppo A6 Pro 5G , 6.57-inch AMOLED display with 120Hz refresh rate delivers vibrant. Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 6300 chipset and 8GB RAM, the Oppo A6 Pro 5G. The 50MP + 2MP dual rear camera and 16MP front camera capture sharp, detailed photos and videos With 5G, Wi-Fi 5, Bluetooth 5.4, NFC, \r\nOPPO A6 Pro 5G is a powerhouse for users looking for 5G connectivity, massive battery, durable build, and smooth performance in Bangladesh 2025.\r\n', 'Oppo A6 Pro 5G is an impressive smartphone that perfectly balances performance, battery life, and durability. Thanks to its 5G connectivity, massive 7000mAh battery, and 80W SUPERVOOC fast charging, it keeps you going all day without interruptions. Its sturdy and stylish design makes it reliable for everyday use, while the powerful MediaTek Dimensity 6300 processor ensures smooth performance for apps, multitasking, and gaming. Priced at BDT 34,990 in Bangladesh, the Oppo A6 Pro 5G offers great value for money, making it an excellent choice for anyone looking for a capable and long-lasting mid-range smartphone.', '2025-10-07 11:46:25'),
(7, 8, 'Tecno Pova 7 Pro Price in Bangladesh October 2025\r\nThe Tecno Pova 7 Pro is available variant (128/256GB/8/12GB RAM). Tecno Pova 7 Pro life long 6000mAh battery with 45W wired and 30W wireless fast charging With 10W reverse charging. Techno Pova 7 pro powered by the Mediatek Dimensity 7300 Ultimate (4 nm) chipset.', 'Tecno Pova 7 Pro 5G is a powerful mid-range 5G smartphone. . Tecno Pova 7 Pro high-performance processing, long-lasting battery life, fast charging, and advanced camera features. Its 144Hz AMOLED display power by MediaTek Dimensity 7300 Ultimate processor makes it perfect for gaming and multitasking. If you are looking for a 5G-supported smartphone with durable battery and premium features at an affordable price, Tecno Pova 7 Pro 5G is an excellent choice in 2025.', '2025-10-07 18:15:10'),
(8, 9, 'The Tecno Spark 40 is a budget smartphone. Tecno Spark 40  support 6.67-inch 120Hz IPS LCD display, perfect for gaming, video, and smooth scrolling. Tecno Spark 40 Powered by MediaTek Helio G81 Octa-core processor. The 50MP AI rear camera and 8MP front camera with dual LED flash. With a 5,200mAh battery and 45W fast charging, enjoy long-lasting battery life and quick recharges. Tecno Spark 40 support os Android 15 with HiOS 15.1, it offers AI tools and face unlock, fingerprint , and a user-friendly interface.', '6GB RAM + 128GB Storage: 13,999taka\r\n8GB RAM + 256GB Storage: 16,499taka\r\n\r\nPros: \r\n120Hz Display: 6.67-inch screen.\r\nLong-lasting Battery: 5,200mAh capacity with 45W fast charging.\r\nAI Features: AI Eraser 2.0, AI Writing, and FreeLink for enhanced user experience.\r\nSplash & Dust Resistance: IP64 rating for added durability.\r\nExpandable Storage: Supports microSD cards for additional space.\r\n\r\nCons:\r\nNo 5G Support: Limited to 4G connectivity.\r\neMMC Storage: May result in slower read/write speeds compared to UFS.\r\nHelio G81 Processor: Not perfect for heavy gaming.\r\n\r\nThe Tecno Spark 40 is a smartphone that gives great value for money. with a 6.67-inch 120Hz display, making videos and games look smooth. The 50MP rear camera and 8MP front camera with dual LED flash take clear photos and bright selfies. Its 5,200mAh battery with 45W fast charging keeps the phone working all day without worries. The phone runs on Android 15 with HiOS 15.1 and includes useful AI features like FreeLink, AI Writing, and AI Eraser. It also has dual SIM support, microSD expansion, and IP64 dust & splash resistance. While it does not support 5G and is not for heavy gaming, it is perfect for everyday use, social media, and entertainment. In Bangladesh, the price starts from 13,999taka to 16,499taka, making it an excellent choice for budget-conscious users.\r\n', '2025-10-08 07:15:24'),
(9, 10, 'The Tecno Pova Slim 5G is slim lightweight 5G smartphone. Tecno Pova Slim  6.78-inch AMOLED 144Hz display and a 50MP dual rear camera. Tecno Pova Slim Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 6400 5G+ chipset with 8GB RAM and 128GB/256GB storage, it ensures smooth performance and efficient multitasking. Tecno include Ella AI Assistant, Dynamic Mood Light, MIL-STD 810H durability, and Dolby Atmos stereo speakers. Tecno Pova Slim 5160mAh battery with 45W wired fast charging .\r\nSlim is a stylish design, powerful battery, high-refresh display, the Tecno Pova Slim 5G is a mid-range 5G smartphone in Bangladesh 2025.\r\n', 'The Tecno Pova Slim 5G 8GB RAM + 256GB storage variant of the Tecno Pova Slim 5G is priced at around 29,999 taka.', '2025-10-08 10:50:18'),
(10, 11, 'Tecno Pova Curve 5G is a mid-range smartphone in Bangladesh with a 6.78-inch AMOLED curved display, 144Hz refresh rate, and MediaTek Dimensity 7300 Ultra processor. Tecno Pova Curve 5G offers 8GB RAM + 128GB internal storage, 64MP + 2MP dual rear camera, and a 13MP front selfie camera with 4K video recording. Tecno Pova Curve 5G Powered by a 5500mAh battery with 45W fast charging, Wi-Fi 6, Bluetooth 5.4, NFC, along with in-display fingerprint sensor and face unlock.', 'Tecno Pova Curve 5G and 64MP dual camera, 6.78\" AMOLED display, and 5500mAh battery. Ideal for gaming, multimedia, and 5G connectivity without breaking the budget.', '2025-10-08 15:57:42'),
(11, 12, 'Apple iPhone 17 Pro Max in Bangladesh 2025 with 12GB RAM, up to 2TB storage, 6.9-inch Super Retina XDR OLED display, and triple 48MP cameras. Experience Face ID security, iOS 26 smooth performance, and premium design. Check the latest iPhone 17 Pro Max price in Bangladesh and features now.', 'The iPhone 17 Pro Max starts from BDT 200,000 for the 256GB model in Bangladesh. you want more storage, the 512GB, 1TB, and 2TB versions go up to BDT 289,999. Considering its stunning design, super-smooth performance, and powerful cameras, itâ€™s a great choice for anyone looking for a premium smartphone in 2025.', '2025-10-09 06:12:10'),
(12, 13, 'Xiaomi Redmi 15 5G Bangladesh 6.9-inch HD+ IPS display adaptive brightness Snapdragon 6s Gen 3 5G 64-bit octa-core processor Adreno GPU 6GB or 8GB RAM 128GB or 256GB UFS 2.2 storage microSD expandable 50MP main camera 8MP front camera night mode HDR 5000mAh battery fast charging fingerprint sensor face unlock available in Gray Sandy Blue Red colors 5G and 4G network support budget smartphone Bangladesh with smooth performance and stylish design', 'Xiaomi Redmi 15 5G Bangladesh price starts from BDT 21000 for 6GB 128GB variant and BDT 25,999 for 8GB 256GB variant', '2025-10-11 15:09:25'),
(13, 14, 'Xiaomi 17 Pro Max 2025 in Bangladesh 6.9-inch  LTPO AMOLED display, Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5, 12GB/16GB RAM, 512GB/1TB storage, triple 50MP cameras, 7500mAh battery, and fast charging.', '12GB RAM + 512GB Storage: 129,500BDT/\r\n16GB RAM + 512GB Storage: 136,500BDT/\r\n6GB RAM + 1TB Storage: 148,500BDT', '2025-10-12 16:54:48'),
(14, 15, 'Apple iPhone 17 Air 5G smartphone in Bangladesh. 6.3-inch Super Retina XDR OLED display with 120Hz Refresh for smooth scrolling. Powered by  Apple A19 Bionic chip and 8GB RAM, iPhone 17 Air perfect for gaming, multitasking, and daily use. Available in 256GB, 512GB, and 1TB storage variants, iPhone Air model variant color in Space Black, Cloud White, Light Gold, and Sky Blue. Single rear camera 48MP and a 18MP front camera with Face ID for unlocking. 3149 mAh battery with 20W fast charging. iPhone 17 Air offers a premium mobile experience in Bangladesh.', 'Apple has not yet officially released the iPhone 17 Air in Bangladesh. However, unofficial stock is available in some showrooms.', '2025-10-12 20:00:32'),
(15, 17, 'The Vivo Y21d is an affordable smartphone 6,500mAh battery, 50MP primary rear camera, 6.68-inch 90Hz display . IP68 and IP69+ certification, making it dustproof and water-resistant. Android 15 with Funtouch OS 15, powered by the Unisoc T7200 chipset, paired with 6GB/8GB RAM and 128GB internal storage, expandable up to 2TB via microSD. 44W fast Charge. Available in Jade Green and Coral Red, the Vivo Y21d is priced starting at BDT 18,999 in Bangladesh.', '6GB+128GB=1899BDT/ 8GB+128GB=20999BDT', '2025-10-13 17:29:03'),
(16, 18, 'The Realme P3 Lite 5G is a 6.67-inch IPS LCD Display with 120Hz refresh rate. Powered by MediaTek Dimensity 6300 chipset and 4GB/6GB RAM.It comes with 128GB UFS 2.2 storage, expandable via microSD. Realme P3 Lite 32MP rear camera and an 8MP front camera for clear photos and selfies. by a 6000mAh battery with 45W fast charging, IP64 splash resistance, Running Android 15 with Realme UI 6.0, it supports 5G, dual SIM, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth 5.3, with a side-mounted fingerprint sensor and Face Unlock for security.', 'Expectd Price 15,000 BDT for 4GB+128GB', '2025-10-13 19:35:47'),
(17, 16, 'The Vivo Y31 5G is a smartphone Powered by the Snapdragon 4 Gen 2 processor with 6,500 mAh battery with 44W fast charging, it ensures smooth performance and long-lasting usage. The 6.68-inch 120Hz display, Vivo Y31 50MP rear camera and 8MP front camera capture stunning photos and videos. With IP68/IP69 water and dust resistance, Android 15, and 128GB storage with RAM 6GB, Available in Bangladesh for around 22,000BDTâ€“27,000BDT, Vivo Y31 5G .', 'Expected Price: Approximately 20,000BDT/  \r\nAvailable Variants: 4GB RAM + 128GB storage / \r\n6GB RAM + 128GB storage/\r\n Release Date: September 13, 2025/\r\nOfficial Price: 22,000BDT for the 4GB variant', '2025-10-14 15:37:13'),
(18, 19, 'The Samsung Galaxy F17 5G is powerful budget-friendly smartphone, launched in Bangladesh in September 2025. Featuring a 6.7-inch FHD+ Super AMOLED display, Exynos 1330 processor, and triple rear cameras (50MP + 5MP + 2MP), Samsung Galaxy F17 smooth performance for gaming, multitasking, and photography. 5000mAh battery with 25W fast charging, 5G connectivity, and Android 15 with One UI 7. Samsung Galaxy F17 Available in Violet Pop and Neo Black, the Galaxy F17 high-performance 5G smartphone in Bangladesh.', 'Samsung Galaxy F17 5G is priced around BDT 22,000 for the 6GB RAM + 128GB storage variant in Bangladesh.', '2025-10-14 16:31:45'),
(19, 21, 'The Oppo A6i smartphone launched in September 2025. 6.6-inch Full HD+ display with a 120Hz refresh rate, HDR support, and 1000 nits brightness. Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 6300 chipset with an Octa-core CPU and Mali-G57 GPU, it delivers smooth performance for gaming and multitasking. Oppo A6i comes with 8 GB RAM and 128/256 GB internal storage, expandable via microSDXC.\r\nOppo A6i features a 50 MP primary camera with LED flash, digital zoom, and 4K video recording, and 8 MP selfie camera. Oppo A6i runs Android 15 with ColorOS 15.\r\nOppo A6i 6,000 mAh battery with 33w fast charging , Available in White and Black. Oppo A6i is the best choices for mid-range smartphones in Bangladesh.\r\n', 'Oppo A6i (8GB RAM + 128GB Storage): Approximately 18,000BDT/ \r\n\r\nOppo A6i (8GB RAM + 256GB Storage): Approximately 25,000BDT', '2025-10-14 17:43:46'),
(20, 22, 'The Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 5G smartphone officially available in Bangladesh in 2025. It comes with a stunning Super AMOLED display 120Hz refresh rate and HDR10+. Powered by the Snapdragon processor with up to 12GB RAM and 1TB storage, Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra ensures smooth performance for gaming multitasking and productivity. Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra boasts a high-resolution 200MP primary camera . Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra also features a long-lasting 5000mAh battery with fast 45W charging and wireless charging support. Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra is officially priced in Bangladesh', 'Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra is officially priced in Bangladesh starting from BDT 1,79,999 for the base variant with 12GB RAM and 256GB storage. Higher-end variants with 12GB RAM and 512GB or 1TB storage', '2025-10-16 18:56:25'),
(21, 23, 'The Samsung Galaxy S25 is the latest smartphone from Samsung, launched on February 3, 2025, combining stunning design, next-level performance, and cutting-edge technology. It is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite (3 nm) processor, ensuring lightning-fast speed, smooth multitasking, and exceptional gaming performance.\r\nThe Samsung Galaxy S25 features a 6.2-inch LTPO AMOLED 2X display with a 120Hz refresh rate and 2600 nits peak brightness, providing an ultra-smooth and vivid visual experience. Built with Gorilla Glass Victus 2 on both sides and an aluminum frame, the Galaxy S25 offers a durable and premium feel.\r\nSamsung Galaxy S25, 50MP main sensor, 10MP telephoto lens (3x optical zoom), and 12MP ultrawide lens â€” delivering professional-grade photo and video quality. The 12MP front camera ensures clear and detailed selfies. The Galaxy S25 also supports 8K video recording with optical image stabilization for shake-free footage.\r\nPowering the device is a 4,000 mAh battery with 25W fast charging and 15W wireless charging (Qi2) support, keeping you powered throughout the day. It runs on Android 15 (One UI 7), offering improved AI features and smoother user experience.\r\nIn terms of connectivity, the Galaxy S25 includes 5G, Wi-Fi 7, Bluetooth 5.4, NFC, and dual SIM (Nano + eSIM) support. The device also comes with IP68 water and dust resistance, and a fast ultrasonic in-display fingerprint sensor for added security.\r\nWith its stylish design, flagship performance, and advanced camera system, the Samsung Galaxy S25 stands out as one of the best 5G smartphones in Bangladesh for 2025.\r\n', 'Samsung Galaxy S25 (12GB RAM + 128GB storage): Approximately BDT 75,000 \r\n\r\nSamsung Galaxy S25 Ultra (12GB RAM + 256GB storage): Approximately BDT 109,500', '2025-10-17 19:16:07'),
(22, 24, 'The Xiaomi 15 Ultra is the latest smartphone from Xiaomi, designed for those power, performance, and photography excellence. It features a stunning 6.73-inch Quad-Curved AMOLED 2K display with a smooth 120Hz refresh rate and durable Gorilla Glass protection, ensuring an immersive and durable viewing experience.\r\n\r\nPowered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, Xiaomi 15 Ultra phone runs on Android 15 with Xiaomiâ€™s new HyperOS 2, delivering ultra-fast performance and intelligent system optimization. The Xiaomi 15 Ultra stands out with its advanced quad-camera setup, including a 50MP main sensor with OIS, a 50MP telephoto lens (3.2x optical zoom), a 200MP periscope telephoto camera, and a 50MP ultra-wide lensâ€”perfect for professional-grade photography. On the front, the 32MP selfie camera ensures crystal-clear self-portraits.\r\nWith an IP68 rating, the Xiaomi 15 Ultra is both dust and water-resistant, making it durable for daily use. It supports 90W fast wired charging and 80W wireless charging, ensuring quick power-ups for all-day use.\r\n\r\nIn Bangladesh, the Xiaomi 15 Ultra price is BDT 160,000 (Unofficial) for the 16GB RAM and 512GB storage variant, making it a premium choice for users seeking flagship-level performance, photography, and design.\r\n', 'Pros for Price:\r\n1. Flagship-level performance\r\n2. Industry-leading camera setup\r\n3. Premium display & design\r\n4. Super-fast charging\r\n\r\nCons for Price:\r\n1. Expensive for the average user\r\n2. No official warranty (unofficial model)\r\n\r\nVerdict:\r\nAt BDT 160,000, the Xiaomi 15 Ultra is a strong competitor in the flagship segment, especially for users who prioritize camera quality, performance, and premium design.\r\n', '2025-10-18 18:57:12'),
(23, 25, 'The OnePlus 13 is a flagship smartphone released in November 2024, offering powerful performance and a premium design. It comes in two variants 12GB+256GB and 16GB+512GB with the main difference being in RAM, storage, and price. The phone features a large 6.82-inch LTPO AMOLED display with 1440Ã—3168 resolution and a 120Hz refresh rate, ensuring smooth visuals and excellent color accuracy.\r\nPowered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, the OnePlus 13 delivers top-tier gaming and multitasking performance. Its triple rear camera setup includes a 50MP Sony main sensor, 50MP periscope telephoto lens (3x optical zoom), and 50MP ultra-wide lens, while the 32MP front camera ensures sharp selfies and clear video calls.\r\nThe device is backed by a 6000mAh battery that supports 100W fast wired charging and 50W wireless charging , making it ideal for heavy users. In Bangladesh, the unofficial price of the OnePlus 13 (16GB+512GB) is  BDT 129,500. Overall, the OnePlus 13 stands out as a premium choice for users seeking excellent display quality, strong performance, long battery life, and professional-grade cameras.\r\n', 'The price of the OnePlus 13 (16GB+512GB) in Bangladesh is around BDT 129,500 (Unofficial), while the 12GB+256GB version costs approximately BDT 111,000â€“115,000. Official prices may vary depending on availability, import costs, and store location.\r\nUnofficial Price (16GB+512GB): BDT 129,500\r\nUnofficial Price (12GB+256GB): BDT 111,000â€“115,000\r\nOfficial Price (Expected): To be announced soon\r\n', '2025-10-21 14:56:02'),
(24, 26, 'The Google Pixel 10 is set to launch at the Made by Google event in New York City on August 20, 2025, at 1 PM. This flagship device will be part of the Pixel 10 series, which includes three other smartphones, including the standard Pixel 10.\r\nThe Pixel 10 Pro comes with Material 3 Expressive UI, offering a smooth and customizable user interface. Powered by the Google Tensor G5 chip, it ensures high performance, AI-driven features, and enhanced battery efficiency.\r\nTriple rear camera system for stunning photography.\r\nLarge AMOLED display with high resolution and refresh rate.\r\nAI tools like Magic Cue, Daily Hub, and Ask Photos for a smarter user experience.\r\nCustomizable Quick Settings and Gestures for ease of use.\r\nThe Google Pixel 10 Pro price in Bangladesh is expected to be competitive, making it one of the most anticipated Android smartphones of 2025. Users in Bangladesh can look forward to advanced AI features, superior design, and a premium mobile experience.\r\n', 'The Google Pixel 10  is available in Bangladesh through various unofficial retailers, with prices varying based on storage configurations:\r\n16GB RAM + 128GB Storage: BDT 137,000 \r\n16GB RAM + 256GB Storage: Approximately  BDT-143,000\r\n16GB RAM + 512GB Storage: Approximately BDT-167,000\r\n16GB RAM + 1TB Storage: Approximately BDT-170,000\r\nThese prices are for the unofficial models, as the official launch in Bangladesh has not occurred yet.\r\n', '2025-10-21 16:20:18'),
(25, 27, 'The Samsung Galaxy A17 5G is a budget friendly smartphone available in Bangladesh offering a perfect balance of performance, camera quality, and long lasting battery life. It features a large 6.7 inch Super AMOLED display with 90Hz refresh rate ensuring smooth. Powered by the Exynos 1330 chipset, the Galaxy A17 5G handles tasks and light gaming efficiently.\r\nSamsung Galaxy A17 5G it comes with a 50MP main camera with OIS for clear and detailed images in both day and night conditions, and a 13MP front camera ideal for selfies and social media sharing. Samsung Galaxy A17 5G offers multiple RAM and storage options including 6GB or 8GB RAM and 128GB or 512GB storage, expandable via microSD.\r\nEquipped with a 5000mAh battery supporting 25W fast charging, the Samsung Galaxy A17 5G ensures long hours of usage without frequent charging. Running on Android 15 with One UI 7, it provides a user friendly interface and long term software update support.\r\n', 'Official Price: BDT 24,999 (6GB RAM + 128GB storage)\r\nUnofficial Price: Starting from BDT 23,999\r\nVariants:\r\n6GB RAM + 128GB storage\r\n8GB RAM + 128GB storage\r\n8GB RAM + 256GB storage\r\n', '2025-10-21 18:33:21'),
(26, 28, 'The Vivo X300 Pro is a flagship 5G smartphone powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 9500 (3nm) chipset for smooth gaming and fast performance. It features a 6.78-inch 120Hz AMOLED display, a 200MP periscope camera, and a 6510mAh battery with 90W fast charging. With up to 16GB RAM and 1TB storage, it delivers a premium experience for gamers and photographers alike. The Vivo X300 Pro price in Bangladesh makes it one of the best choices for performance, camera, and design lovers in 2025.', 'The price & variants for the Vivo X300 Pro in Bangladesh:\r\nRAM 12 GB + Storage 256 GB: à§³ 115,000 (unofficial market) \r\nRAM 16 GB + Storage 512 GB: à§³ 130,000 (unofficial market)\r\n', '2025-10-21 19:21:20'),
(27, 29, 'The Vivo V60e is a premium mid-range smartphone . 200MP main camera, capturing ultra-clear and highly detailed photos. Coupled with the 50MP front camera.\r\nThe 6.77-inch AMOLED display with a 20:9 aspect ratio and Full HD+ resolution (1080 x 2392 pixels) ensures vivid colors, deep contrasts, and immersive visuals. Its 120Hz refresh rate enhances scrolling, gaming, and video playback. \r\nMediaTek Dimensity 7360 Turbo chipset powers the Vivo V60e, ensuring smooth multitasking, gaming, and daily usage. The device offers 8GB or 12GB RAM options along with 128GB or 256GB internal storage.\r\nThe 6500mAh battery, which supports long-lasting usage day.the 90W fast charging ensures you can recharge the phone quickly. The Vivo V60e runs on Android 15 with .\r\nThe Vivo V60e price in Bangladesh starts at approximately BDT 40,000 for the base model. Compared to other mid-range smartphones, the Vivo V60e offers exceptional value, balancing high-resolution cameras, AMOLED display, long-lasting battery, and fast performance.\r\n', 'The Vivo V60e is priced at around BDT 40,000 in Bangladesh. It features a 200MP main camera, 50MP front camera, 6.77-inch AMOLED display, 120Hz refresh rate, MediaTek Dimensity 7360 chipset, and a 6500mAh battery with 90W fast charging. The Vivo V60e for its smooth performance, immersive display, and long-lasting battery, making it a top choice in the mid-range smartphone segment.', '2025-10-23 17:37:18'),
(28, 30, 'The Vivo V60 is one of the most stunning smartphones now available in Bangladesh. Powered by the Snapdragon 7 Gen 4 processor, it delivers lightning-fast speed for gaming, multitasking, and daily use. Vivo V60 6.67-inch AMOLED display with a smooth 120Hz refresh rate.\r\nThe Vivo V60 powerful 50MP Sony main camera and a 32MP front shooter, the Vivo V60 ensures crystal-clear photos and flawless selfies every time. The phone comes in multiple variants, including 8GB/128GB and 12GB/256GB, giving users enough space for everything they need. Backed by a massive 6500mAh battery and 90W Flash Charging.\r\nThe Vivo V60 5G features a sleek curved AMOLED design, in-display fingerprint sensor, and IP68 water and dust resistance. Available in attractive colors like Dazzle, Berry Purple, and Mist Grey, this model perfectly blends power and elegance.\r\n', 'The Vivo V60 price in Bangladesh starts from à§³52,000 to à§³64,999, depending on the variant. Snapdragon 7 Gen 4 processor, 50MP Sony camera, and 90W fast charging, Overall, the Vivo V60 is a stylish, powerful, and value-packed 5G smartphone for 2025.', '2025-10-23 18:27:51'),
(29, 31, 'The Motorola Moto G6 is a mid-range smartphone with a 5.7-inch Full HD+ 18:9 display and sleek design. Powered by the Mediatek Helio G81 Ultra processor with 3GB/4GB RAM and 32GB/64GB internal storage. The dual rear camera setup (12MP + 5MP) and 8MP front camera deliver impressive photography, while the 7000mAh battery. Running Android v15.', 'The Motorola Moto G6 price in Bangladesh starts around BDT 15,000â€“17,000(official), offering great value for its 18:9 display, Mediatek Helio G81 processor, and dual cameras. Itâ€™s an affordable choice for users seeking performance and style on a budget.', '2025-10-23 19:29:26'),
(30, 32, 'Samsung Galaxy S22 Plus Used Phone â€“ Premium Features at an Affordable Price in Bangladesh.\r\nLooking to buy a used phone that delivers flagship performance without stretching your budget? The Samsung Galaxy S22 Plus is one of the top choices for anyone in Bangladesh searching for a pre-owned phone with cutting-edge features.\r\nThis used Samsung Galaxy S22 Plus comes with a stunning 6.6-inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X display and a smooth 120Hz refresh rate, offering vibrant visuals for gaming, streaming, and daily tasks. Its triple camera system, featuring a 50MP primary sensor, 10MP telephoto lens with 3Ã— optical zoom, and 12MP ultrawide lens, ensures crisp photos, professional-quality shots, and even 8K video recording. Whether youâ€™re a content creator or someone who loves premium photography, this used phone wonâ€™t disappoint.\r\nWith the used phone price in Bangladesh being highly competitive, the Galaxy S22 Plus offers a perfect balance of performance and affordability. Donâ€™t miss the chance to own a high-end second hand phone that feels as good as new while saving money. Explore the second hand phone price in Bangladesh today and upgrade your mobile experience with the Samsung Galaxy S22 Plus!\r\n', 'Why Choose This?\r\nâ€¢	Affordable compared to other used phone prices in Bangladesh.\r\nâ€¢	A well-conditioned second hand phone usually costs much less than a brand-new device.\r\nâ€¢	Premium display, powerful camera, and flagship-level performance.\r\nâ€¢	A perfect budget-friendly choice for those looking to buy a used phone.\r\nCaution\r\nâ€¢	Check the battery health.\r\nâ€¢	Inspect the screen, back glass, and camera condition.\r\nâ€¢	Verify if there have been any previous repairs.\r\nâ€¢	Ensure warranty and IMEI verification.\r\nSummary\r\nThe Samsung Galaxy S22 Plus is a pre-owned phone offering flagship features at a budget-friendly price. If you check its condition before purchasing, it provides excellent value for money according to second hand phone prices in Bangladesh.\r\n', '2025-10-30 15:47:49'),
(31, 33, 'The Redmiâ€¯K90â€¯Proâ€¯Max is a 6.9â€‘inch 2K OLED display with 120â€¯Hz refresh rate, delivering ultraâ€‘smooth gaming. It uses powerful Snapdragonâ€¯8â€¯Elite Genâ€¯5 processor, 12â€¯GB RAM and 250GB storage. Its camera system includes a 50â€¯MP main sensor with OIS, a 50â€¯MP periscope telephoto with 5Ã— optical zoom, and a 50â€¯MP ultraâ€‘wide lens, ensuring you capture highâ€‘quality photos and videos in any scenario. The phone 7,560â€¯mAh battery, supporting 100â€¯W wired charging, 50â€¯W wireless charging, and 22.5â€¯W reverse charging. HyperOSâ€¯3 based on Androidâ€¯16 The best gaming phone 2025-Redmiâ€¯K90â€¯Proâ€¯Max specs-Redmiâ€¯K90â€¯Proâ€¯Max price in Bangladesh.', 'The 12â€‰GBâ€¯+â€¯256â€‰GB variant is unofficially listed at à§³ 84,900. \r\nThe 12â€‰GBâ€¯+â€¯512â€‰GB variant is unofficially priced around à§³ 94,900. \r\nOne source mentions a price as low as à§³ 78,000 in some cases (still unofficial)\r\n', '2025-11-01 18:03:11'),
(32, 34, 'iQOO Neo 11 is a premium smartphone, designed for gamers and power users. The phone features a 6.78-inch LTPO AMOLED display, 144Hz refresh rate and 20:9 aspect ratio -\r\nThe phone uses the Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, which offers excellent performance in gaming, video editing and multitasking. Up to 12GB of RAM and 256GB of UFS 4.0 storage make the phone fast and responsive for a long time.\r\nIn the camera section, the iQOO Neo 11 has a 50MP OIS main sensor, which is capable of retaining excellent details and colors during the day. The software-optimization also performs well in night shots, even though it is primarily a gaming-focused phone.\r\nBattery performance includes a 5000mAhâ€“7500mAh cell and 100W fast charging, which charges up to 50% in just a few minutes. The phone has a brightness of around 4500 nits, so the screen is very clear even when used in sunlight.\r\nIn terms of design, it is slim, sleek and gives a premium look. The latest connectivity options are included, including 5G, Wi-Fi 6, Bluetooth 5.3, NFC.', 'The iQOO Neo 11 price in Bangladesh is expected to be around 50,000takaâ€“55,000taka depending on the variant.', '2025-11-04 17:40:20'),
(33, 35, 'Realme C85 Pro comes with a brand new design and great performance. The phone has a 6.8-inch AMOLED Full HD+ display with 120Hz refresh rate, which makes the visual experience smoother and more premium. The Snapdragon 685 chipset, 8GB LPDDR4x RAM (up to 24GB with Dynamic Expansion), and UFS 2.2 storage make gaming, browsing, and multitasking run at lightning speed. The 50MP AI dual camera system produces clear and natural images, and the massive 7000 mAh battery supports 45W fast chargingâ€”meaning worry-free use all day long. With IP69 Pro water and dust resistance and affordable price, the Realme C85 Pro is now a â€œFlagship Killerâ€ in the mid-range market of Bangladesh.', '6GB+128GB=20999BDT\r\n8GB+128GB=22999BDT\r\n8GB+256GB=24999BDT\r\n', '2025-11-05 12:26:59'),
(34, 39, 'The Motorola Moto G67 Power price in Bangladesh makes it one of the most attractive mid-range smartphones for budget-conscious buyers. With the Moto G67 Power BD price offering great value, it is ideal for users who want a reliable daily phone without spending a fortune. The official price BD confirms that the phone combines affordability with impressive features. Featuring a massive 7000mAh battery, the Moto G67 Power battery life easily lasts for two to three days, making it perfect for heavy users, travelers, and those who rely on social media or streaming apps throughout the day. Along with 30W fast charging, the device ensures quick top-ups, keeping downtime to a minimum.\r\n\r\nAs a Moto G67 Power 5G phone in Bangladesh, it delivers smooth performance for casual gaming, multitasking, and browsing. The Moto G67 Power full specifications highlight a 6.7-inch FHD+ display, a 50MP main camera, ultrawide lens, and a 32MP selfie camera, making it suitable for everyday photography and video creation. Reviews of the Moto G67 Power camera and gaming performance show that while it is not a flagship gaming phone, it handles moderate games and daily photography tasks efficiently.\r\n\r\nUsers looking for Moto G67 Power pros and cons can rest assured that the device balances durability, performance, and battery life. With features like dual stereo speakers, 3.5mm headphone jack, and IP64 water-dust protection, it provides excellent value for casual users. The Moto G67 Power antutu benchmark and performance score indicate reliable day-to-day performance, while Moto G67 Power online price BD and shop price BD make it accessible to buyers across Bangladesh. Positive user opinion BD highlights the long-lasting battery, smooth interface, and practical features. Overall, the Moto G67 Power value for money and its reputation as one of the best phones under 30000 in Bangladesh make it a smart and practical choice for anyone seeking a dependable, battery-focused mid-range smartphone.', 'The Motorola Moto G67 Power is priced around à§³23,000â€“30,000 in Bangladesh, offering strong value for money. Its 7000mAh battery ensures 2â€“3 days of usage on a single charge, perfect for heavy daily use. The Snapdragon mid-range processor handles multitasking and casual gaming smoothly. While the camera performs well in daylight, it is not a flagship-level photography device.', '2025-11-27 15:38:51'),
(35, 40, 'The oppo reno 14f 5G is a budget friendly smartphone available in Bangladesh offering a perfect balance of performance, camera quality, and long lasting battery life. It features a large 6.57 inch Super AMOLED display with 120Hz refresh rate ensuring smooth. Powered by the Snapdragon 6 Gen 1 chipset.\r\noppo reno 14f A17 5G it comes with a 50MP main camera with OIS for clear and detailed images in both day and night conditions, and a 32MP front camera ideal for selfies and social media sharing. oppo reno 14f 5G offers multiple RAM and storage options including 8GB RAM and 256GB storage.\r\nEquipped with a 6000mAh battery supporting 45W fast charging, the oppo reno 14f ensures long hours of usage without frequent charging. Running on Android 15, it provides a user friendly interface and long term software update support.', 'The OPPO Reno 14F 5G is priced at around 39,990for the 8GB RAM + 256GB storage variant in Bangladesh. Some stores may offer the 12GB RAM + 512GB storage variant at a higher price.', '2025-11-28 06:01:02'),
(36, 41, 'The Realme gt8 pro 5G is a 6.79-inch LTPO AMOLED Display with 144Hz refresh rate. Powered by Qualcomm SM8850-AC Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5 chipset and 12GB RAM.It comes with 256GB and 512 GB UFS 4.1 storage, expandable via microSD. Realme Gt8 pro 50MP rear camera and an 32MP front camera for clear photos and selfies. by a 7000mAh battery with 120W fast charging, IP68/IP69 resistance, Running Android 16 with Realme UI 7.0, it supports 5G, dual SIM, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth 6.0, with a On-screen fingerprint sensor and Face Unlock for security.', 'The Realme gt8 pro is priced around à§³80,000 in Bangladesh, offering strong value for money. Its 7000mAh battery ensures 2â€“3 days of usage on a single charge, perfect for heavy daily use. The Snapdragon high-range processor handles multitasking and casual gaming smoothly. While the camera performs well in daylight, it is a flagship-level graming device.', '2025-11-28 06:52:09'),
(37, 42, 'The Lava Agni 4 is a powerful and feature-packed 5G smartphone. It comes with a stunning 6.67-inch 1.5K AMOLED display offering a 120Hz refresh rate, HDR support, and up to 2400 nits brightness. Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 8350 processor, 8GB LPDDR5X RAM, and 256GB UFS 4.0 storage, Its clean, stock-like Android 15. the Agni 4 features a dual rear camera setup with a 50MP OIS primary lens and an 8MP ultra-wide camera, along with a 50MP 4K-ready front camera stable video recording. The 5000mAh battery with 66W fast charging, modern features like Wi-Fi 6E, Bluetooth 5.4, Type-C 3.2, an in-display fingerprint sensor, and a customizable Action Key enhance overall usability.', 'The Lava Agni 4 is priced around â‚¹24,998 in India and approximately 35,000BDTâ€“43,900BDT in Bangladesh, offering strong mid-range value. With its AMOLED display, 5G support, and fast charging, it delivers excellent performance for the price.', '2025-11-30 07:10:22'),
(38, 43, 'The Oppo Find X9 is 5G smartphone designed for high performance, premium build, and superior photography. Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 9500 chipset, it for gaming, multitasking, and creative apps. Its 6.59-inch 120Hz AMOLED display\r\nthe triple 50MP camera system. The 7025mAh battery ensures long-lasting usage, while fast charging. Built with glass and aluminum, the Oppo Find X9 is stylish, durable, and water/dust resistant.\r\nAI photography, 4K video recording, and full 5G network support, the Oppo Find X9 is a future-proof device ideal for students\r\n', 'The Oppo Find X9 is priced around 124,500 in Bangladesh\r\nConsidering its MediaTek Dimensity 9500 chipset, 5G support, and triple 50MP cameras, it delivers excellent value for premium users\r\n', '2025-12-05 19:57:39');
